{"tid":1479204,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"北美圍爐取暖區","createTime":"2019-08-16T20:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T02:11:26.000Z","uid":102302,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2445c486728c28b984a5cb768eac8a6b3464fe89","tid":1479204,"uid":102302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T20:30:28.000Z","msg":"小弟平時係cdrom 今日第一次出po<br />\n宜家喺加州生活緊<br />\n香港發生咁多事好唔開心<br />\n但係自己整係做到鍵盤戰士<br />\n每日努力文宣<br />\n想開個telegram group圍爐取暖<br />\n@md077711727<br />\n<br />\n香港加油"},{"pid":"4bd5ed80a8e3160a97adc8327357114e550a25b6","tid":1479204,"uid":102302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2445c486728c28b984a5cb768eac8a6b3464fe89","tid":1479204,"uid":102302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T20:30:28.000Z","msg":"小弟平時係cdrom 今日第一次出po<br />\n宜家喺加州生活緊<br />\n香港發生咁多事好唔開心<br />\n但係自己整係做到鍵盤戰士<br />\n每日努力文宣<br />\n想開個telegram group圍爐取暖<br />\n@md077711727<br />\n<br />\n香港加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T20:44:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33903ec2b24b110056b7dcc818399e0351b0106f","tid":1479204,"uid":75232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T21:17:36.000Z","msg":"全球聲討八一一警暴，與港同行集會<br />\n<br />\n*呼籲參加者自行準備各式標語及穿著黑色上衣*<br />\n<br />\n*對公開身份有顧慮者請自行準備適當衣著*<br />\n<br />\n* English version follows *<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n八月十一日，香港警察妄顧市民生命安全，在香港多處地方施放催淚彈、使用不合理武力、及濫捕，以致多人受傷，甚至有女示威者被布袋彈擊中以致永久失明，人神共憤！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n北加州香港會將會聯同香港大專學界、全球港人團體、連登「我要攬炒」、「Stand With Hong Kong」團隊、及民陣等，於今個星期六，八月十七日下午二時，在三藩市 Embarcadero Plaza 舉行集會，聲討警暴，堅守五大訴求，支持美國國會通過「香港人權民主法案」，與港人同行到底。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時間：八月十七日(星期六)下午二時至三時半<br />\n<br />\n地點：Embarcadero Plaza, San Francisco, CA 94105<br />\n<br />\n網頁：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/2267058620224525/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F2267058620224525%2F&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75XKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=9f4de72d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/2267058620224525/</a><br />\n<br />\n泊車資訊：<br />\n<br />\n\t最近：Four Embarcadero Center (<a href=\"https://lots.impark.com/imp#details=27,77\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flots.impark.com%2Fimp%23details%3D27%2C77&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75XKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=d4b908d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lots.impark.com/imp#details=27,77</a>)<br />\n<br />\n\t次近：Three Embarcadero Center (<a href=\"https://lots.impark.com/imp#details=27,76\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flots.impark.com%2Fimp%23details%3D27%2C76&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75XKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=5be127c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lots.impark.com/imp#details=27,76</a>)<br />\n<br />\n\t隔一街口：Golden Gateway Garage (<a href=\"https://lots.impark.com/imp#details=27,50\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flots.impark.com%2Fimp%23details%3D27%2C50&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75XKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=1dc0fc8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lots.impark.com/imp#details=27,50</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們榮幸邀請到史丹福大學戴雅門教授發表講話及前學民思潮/香港眾志成員黃希憫分享反送中運動親身經歷。我們亦會展示香港現場收集到的催淚彈殼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘉賓簡介：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n戴雅門教授<br />\n<br />\n史丹佛大學政治及社會學教授及胡佛研究院資深研究員、著名政治學者，數十年來專注研究民主轉型，曾於包括大中華地區的全球超過70個國家實地研究。他多年來關心和追蹤著香港的發展變化，曾指導過二十三條立法失敗後前往史丹佛求學的前保安局局長、建制派議員葉劉淑儀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃希憫<br />\n<br />\n加大柏克萊分校政治及歷史雙學位生，Vasconcellos民主行動研究所公共政策倡導員，國際特赦組織助選員，前香港模擬立法會核心成員，前香港眾志立法會助選顧問，前學民思潮成員。"},{"pid":"988da23974bb14207276af4ea12e96c785f5ca33","tid":1479204,"uid":31906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T21:24:06.000Z","msg":"星期六LA 會唔會有活動？"},{"pid":"ce08bd30a2902e2fa4192a4e131b3e251642f58d","tid":1479204,"uid":274289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T21:51:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56791020e49f60a108dd79f7d5690a19da504526","tid":1479204,"uid":102302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"988da23974bb14207276af4ea